t Google Qualified Partners he managed the digital marketing accounts for some of Australia\'s largest travel companies including Accor Group, Roamfree and Westin Hotels Australia.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Working with several of Queenslands most successful startups, he has visited Singapore,&nbsp;San Francisco, London and Melbourne to consult and work with these companies providing user interface and growth hacking services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>During his time at The Various Artists as a founding member, Robert has&nbsp;helped foster Maroochydore as a technology, creative and cultural hub. Running the&nbsp;Sunshine Coast’s first co-working space in the old Maroochydore courthouse.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Robert helps our clients plan, deliver and measure their digital marketing campaigns.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','contact',0,27,27,'und',0,'<p>Our design studio is located on the first floor of&nbsp;\"the old courthouse\" building in Maroochydore. We have great coffee, boardroom facilities and parking is available at the rear. Schedule an appointment or feel free&nbsp;to drop in for a casual chat and a coffee.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html');
