career in the famous \"Listerine Texaco\" livery.Raced by F1 World Champ Damon Hill.CAMS Historic Log Books and race ready.$160K AUD ONO.','full_html'),('node','car',0,689,689,'und',0,'All but brand new1 of only 3 delivered new to Australia1 of 250 made world wideGreat colour combinationOnly 1000K\'s from newOne of the top 3 most stunning road 911\'s EVER. ******Some great pics that do the car a little bit of justice******POA','full_html'),('node','car',0,690,690,'und',0,'Number 009 of 501 worldwide.Only 977 K\'s from new.Upgraded to over 700Hp and 43% more torque.Mark Webber of Redbull F1 fame has one.Insanely fast, yet still a happy about town 911.Looks stunning, in an evil kind of way.Heaps of options and a few spares.','full_html'),('node','car',0,691,691,'und',0,'Owner has done all the hard work, needs finishing to the correct LP standard.Undisputedly the fastest Holden that raced in Group A.Raced in multiple iconic liveries.Full of LP specific \"tricks\".Guaranteed front runner in \"Heritage Touring Cars\"Owner wants out ASAP.$POA','full_html'),('node','car',0,692,692,'und',0,'A genuine Salamanca Red LJ GTR.Excellent chassis with original log books.Very well engineered.HDT Group C A9X spec 308.Gets along at a good rate...Sold','full_html'),('node','car',0,693,693,'und',0,'Jesus raced this car in the Spa 24hr.1987 WTCC history.Qualified P2 at Bathurst 1000 WTCC 1987.Numerous outright wins in France.Only RS500 to have raced as an official FOMOCO works car.Special piece of kit!$POA','full_html'),('node','car',0,694,694,'und',0,'\n* 2001 QLD 500 winner with Steven Johnson/Paul Radisich.\n* Car competed in two seasons of V8\'s; 2001 and 2002.\n* The final evolution of the AU V8 Supercar built by DJR.\n* Never thrashed in the Development Series.\n* Excellent condition in every way.\n$180K AUD FIRM or trades with Porsche, Group C / A, or pre 1967 Shelby.\n ','full_html'),('node','car',0,695,695,'und',0,'\n*Car competed in two seasons of V8 Supercars and two seasons i